# Local dev secrets — copy this to `.dev.vars` and fill in.
# Loaded by:
#   - `wrangler dev` (Cloudflare runtime locals.runtime.env)
#   - `@dotenvx/dotenvx run -f .dev.vars -- <cmd>` (only when --with-db is enabled)
#
# Add DATABASE_HOST / DATABASE_USERNAME / DATABASE_PASSWORD below if you
# ran `pnpm run init-project --with-db`.
